<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-2969] parameter annotations for constructors do not show up in runtime environment</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2969</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Parameter annotations for constructors don&apos;t show up in the runtime environment when specified in groovy code. They work when using java. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NOTE: In the unit test, the CONSTRUCTOR annotation ElementType works for both groovy and java.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NOTE: the only external package dependency is the unit test package, testng.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>mac os x, java version &amp;quot;1.6.0_05&amp;quot;&lt;br/&gt;
intellij 7.0.3&lt;br/&gt;
testng</environment>
